parts.text:
```json
{
"application": "GEOS-Chem",
"details": {
"software": [
"GEOS-Chem Classic",
"HEMCO",
"SLURM",
"LSF",
"Docker",
"git"
],
"resources": [
"CPU",
"Memory",
"Disk Space",
"Network"
],
"dependencies": [
"Bash",
"sed",
"commonFunctionsForTests.sh",
"gcclassic.env",
"cleanRunDir.sh"
],
"environment": [
"OMP_NUM_THREADS",
"OMP_STACKSIZE",
"SLURM_JOBID",
"LSB_JOBID",
"GIT_DISCOVERY_ACROSS_FILESYSTEM"
],
"configuration": {
"scheduler": "SLURM or LSF",
"cores": 24,
"nodes": 1,
"walltime": "0-2:00",
"memory": "90000",
"partition": "REQUESTED_PARTITION",
"docker image": "registry.gsc.wustl.edu/sleong/esm:intel-2021.1.2",
"output": "lsf-%J.txt"
},
"execution": {
"command": "srun -c ${OMP_NUM_THREADS} ./${exeFile} or ./${exeFile}",
"input": "HEMCO_Config.rc",
"output": "results.execute.log",
"logs": "execute.${runDir}.log"
}
}
}
```
